snippet.title: Block Strategy Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Block Strategy is out NOW! 

Block Strategy is a base building RTS, where you need to explore the world to gather resources and defend your base from waves of enemies.

You can purchase at the link below:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2642070/Block_Strategy/
